Package: PHEMLight
Type: Package
Title: Calculate instantaneous vehicle emissions with PHEMLight
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Daniel Rodriguez-Rey <daniel.rodriguez@bsc.es> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: It calculates vehicle specifc power (VSP) from 
    a drive cycle file. According to the emission factors of
    the vehicle fleet provided, to then determine 
    NOx, CO, HC, PM and PN emissions both exhaust and non-exhast 
    (cold-start, resuspension, road, tyre and break wear).
